data.name: YC Female Founder Friday - Zoom Q&A
data.summary: This Friday, three YC Visiting Partners will be answering your questions. They're happy to discuss anything related to starting and building a startup. You'll meet a group of founders that have experience building across a range of verticals (consumer, gaming, construction)
